trans-unit.source: Represents the binding element used to specify an HTTPS transport for transmitting messages.
trans-unit.target: Representa o elemento de associação usado para especificar um transporte HTTPS para transmissão de mensagens.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.HttpsTransportBindingElement> class is the starting point for creating a custom binding that implements the HTTPS transport protocol.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.HttpsTransportBindingElement> classe é o ponto de partida para criar uma associação personalizada que implementa o protocolo de transporte HTTPS.

trans-unit.source: HTTPS is the primary transport used for secure interoperability purposes.
trans-unit.target: HTTPS é o transporte primário usado para fins de interoperabilidade segura.

trans-unit.source: HTTPS is supported by the [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/includes/indigo1-md.md)] to ensure interoperability with other Web services stacks.
trans-unit.target: HTTPS é suportado pelo [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/includes/indigo1-md.md)] para garantir a interoperabilidade com outra Web services pilhas.

trans-unit.source: The [!INCLUDE[indigo2](~/includes/indigo2-md.md)] service model uses this class to create factory objects that implement the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.IChannelFactory> and <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.IChannelListener> interfaces.
trans-unit.target: O [!INCLUDE[indigo2](~/includes/indigo2-md.md)] modelo de serviço usa essa classe para criar objetos de fábrica que implementam o <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.IChannelFactory> e <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.IChannelListener> interfaces.

trans-unit.source: These factory objects, in turn, create the channels and listeners that transmit SOAP messages using the HTTPS protocol.
trans-unit.target: Esses objetos de fábrica, por sua vez, criam os canais e ouvintes que transmitem mensagens SOAP usando o protocolo HTTPS.

trans-unit.source: You control the configuration of the factories that this class creates by setting its properties, such as: <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.HttpsTransportBindingElement.RequireClientCertificate%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Controlar a configuração das fábricas de que essa classe cria definindo suas propriedades, como: <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.HttpsTransportBindingElement.RequireClientCertificate%2A>.

trans-unit.source: You can also set properties on the base class, <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.HttpTransportBindingElement>, such as: <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.HttpTransportBindingElement.AuthenticationScheme%2A>, <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.HttpTransportBindingElement.HostNameComparisonMode%2A>, and <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.HttpTransportBindingElement.MaxBufferSize%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Você também pode definir propriedades na classe base, <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.HttpTransportBindingElement>, tais como: <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.HttpTransportBindingElement.AuthenticationScheme%2A>, <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.HttpTransportBindingElement.HostNameComparisonMode%2A>, e <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.HttpTransportBindingElement.MaxBufferSize%2A>.

trans-unit.source: You can also set properties on the base class <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.TransportBindingElement>, such as: <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.TransportBindingElement.ManualAddressing%2A>, and <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.TransportBindingElement.MaxBufferPoolSize%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Você também pode definir propriedades na classe base <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.TransportBindingElement>, tais como: <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.TransportBindingElement.ManualAddressing%2A>, e <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.TransportBindingElement.MaxBufferPoolSize%2A>.

trans-unit.source: For a complete list of properties, see <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.TransportBindingElement>.
trans-unit.target: Para obter uma lista completa das propriedades, consulte <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.TransportBindingElement>.
